economic activity
has picked up, but there's no
need yet to

03:57.437 --> 03:59.206 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
put on the brakes.

03:59.239 --> 04:02.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANET YELLEN, Federal Reserve
Chair: We're
not seeing strong pressures on
utilization,

04:02.909 --> 04:08.849 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
suggesting overheating, and my
assessment
would be, based on this
evidence, that the

04:08.882 --> 04:15.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
