05:01.468 --> 05:06.106 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KERRY, U.S. Secretary of
State: Now,
this attack has dealt a very
heavy blow to

05:06.139 --> 05:11.011 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
our efforts to bring peace to
Syria, and it
raises a profound doubt about
whether Russia

05:11.044 --> 05:16.316 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and the Assad regime can or will
live up to
the obligations that they agreed
to in Geneva.

05:16.349 --> 05:22.289 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Kerry called for
grounding
all aircraft flying over routes
for humanitarian

05:22.322 --> 05:23.924 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
deliveries.

05:23.957 --> 05:28.828 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Meanwhile, another airstrike hit
a mobile
medical unit outside Aleppo
overnight.

05:28.862 --> 05:32.032 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Activists reported at least 13
people died.

05:32.065 --> 05:37.771 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: President Obama and
Israeli Prime
Minister Benjamin Netanyahu had
a final meeting

05:37.804 --> 05:41.074 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
today at the U.N., after years
of testy relations.

05:41.107 --> 05:43.710 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This time, the two leaders were
all smiles.

05:43.743 --> 05:50.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The president said a new $38
billion military
aid package will let Israel cope
with -- quote

05:50.050 --> 05:52.586 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
-- "enormous uncertainty in the
region."

05:52.619 --> 05:57.724 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The cost of the
emergency allergy
shot EpiPen and the company that
makes it

05:57.757 --> 06:01.228 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
