Congress.

06:01.261 --> 06:07.534 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At a House hearing, Heather
Bresch, CEO of
drugmaker Mylan, defended
raising the price

06:07.567 --> 06:11.104 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
