2007.

06:11.137 --> 06:14.674 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It now costs $608 for a
two-pack.

06:14.708 --> 06:20.146 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
She said Mylan will soon
introduce a generic
version at half the cost, but
lawmakers were

06:20.180 --> 06:21.147 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
unimpressed.

06:21.181 --> 06:22.882 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

06:22.916 --> 06:23.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SCOTT DESJARLAIS (R), Tennessee:
A mother
would cut off her right arm to
get that dose

06:23.817 --> 06:25.652 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
of drug.

06:25.685 --> 06:28.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You decided to charge $600,
instead of cutting
off her arm, and now you're
saying you're

06:28.088 --> 06:31.825 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
dropping it to $300 and that
should make us
all feel better, when, in fact,
that's probably

06:31.858 --> 06:33.693 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
about 10 times what the drug
should cost.

06:33.727 --> 06:36.696 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HEATHER BRESCH, CEO, Mylan:
Congressman, we
want everyone who needs an
EpiPen to have

06:36.730 --> 06:38.531 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
an EpiPen.

06:38.565 --> 06:43.703 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
All the programs that we put in
place, from
the generic, to the higher
patient assistant

06:43.737 --> 06:50.143 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
program, to the co-pay card, so
trying to
address every facet of patient
to make sure

06:50.176 --> 06:54.180 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
they can have access to EpiPen
is what we
will remain focused on.

06:54.214 --> 06:58.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Bresch went on to
say the company
makes $50 profit from each
EpiPen.

06:58.918 --> 07:04.291 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And outside the
Capitol today,
construction crews started work
on the platform

07:04.324 --> 07:09.162 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
