the 45th president
of the United States.

07:09.195 --> 07:14.367 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Republican and Democratic
leaders hammered
in the ceremonial first nails
for the massive

07:14.401 --> 07:20.140 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
10,000-square-foot structure;
1,600 people
will have to fit on the stage.

07:20.173 --> 07:24.911 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Still to come on
the "NewsHour":
we sit down with libertarian
presidential

07:24.944 --> 07:31.217 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
candidate Gary Johnson; Donald
Trump's foreign
business dealings as potential
conflicts of

07:31.251 --> 07:41.294 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
interest; police robots being
