07:49.803 --> 07:54.941 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We return now to the fatal
police shooting
in Charlotte, North Carolina
late yesterday

07:54.974 --> 07:57.977 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and the violent street protests
that followed.

07:58.011 --> 08:00.947 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Here with me now is the city's
mayor, Jennifer
Roberts.

08:00.980 --> 08:02.882 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Welcome, Mayor Roberts.

08:02.916 --> 08:04.150 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Thank you.

08:04.184 --> 08:07.153 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're hearing two different
versions upon
what happened.

08:07.187 --> 08:13.693 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Is there any new information to
come forward
late today that lends credence
to either version?

08:13.727 --> 08:16.162 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS (D), Mayor of
Charlotte,
North Carolina: Well, we have
heard from our

08:16.196 --> 08:20.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
police chief that we do have
video footage
of the incident.

08:20.600 --> 08:22.902 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They are still analyzing it.

08:22.936 --> 08:24.771 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's from different angles.

08:24.804 --> 08:30.343 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have heard that a gun was
found on the
scene, that there was no book
found on the

08:30.377 --> 08:38.184 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
scene, and that we are
corroborating different
witness views as well to make
sure that we

08:38.218 --> 08:40.153 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
have all the facts in hand.

08:40.186 --> 08:44.023 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But we are hearing a very
different story
from within the city.

08:44.057 --> 08:48.628 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You mean from
within the community,
from the relative, or apparently
the daughter

08:48.661 --> 08:54.434 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the victim, and from an
eyewitness who
said she saw a book fall out of
his lap when

08:54.467 --> 08:56.603 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
he got out of the car.

08:56.636 --> 09:01.374 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: We want to
make sure that
we have a thorough
investigation.

09:01.408 --> 09:06.913 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have a history in Charlotte
of being very
transparent, and we absolutely
want the community

09:06.946 --> 09:10.784 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to know that this investigation
will have
the highest integrity.

09:10.817 --> 09:15.555 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We want the community to be
patient as we
put together all the facts.

09:15.588 --> 09:18.792 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We know there are different
versions of the
story out there.

09:18.825 --> 09:24.197 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And we are calling for a
peaceful protest
while we put everything
together, while we

09:24.230 --> 09:25.632 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
get the evidence clear.

09:25.665 --> 09:31.905 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Will the gun that
was found
be publicly released?

09:31.938 --> 09:33.473 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Will it be shown to the public?

09:33.506 --> 09:37.844 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And will that video that we
understand that's
available be shown?

09:37.877 --> 09:43.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: Well, I have
asked to see
the video footage as soon as
possible.

09:43.583 --> 09:46.653 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The chief, at his discretion,
can show it
to leaders in the community.

09:46.686 --> 09:53.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We are working with our officers
to help get
that information to some key
people.

09:53.827 --> 10:01.401 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And absolutely, evidence, once
the investigation
is completed and that we are
sure we have

10:01.434 --> 10:06.639 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
all of it, and it is accurate, I
want us to
be as transparent as possible.

10:06.673 --> 10:13.279 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We absolutely need to show folks
that this
is an investigation that is
transparent with

10:13.313 --> 10:15.181 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the highest integrity.

10:15.215 --> 10:18.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, does that
mean that all
of this material will ultimately
be made available?

10:18.718 --> 10:22.722 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: Well, there
are some legal
issues around that.

10:22.755 --> 10:30.196 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Our policy has been that while
the investigation
is still active, that that is
not made public.

10:30.230 --> 10:36.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But once the investigation is
concluded, whatever
that conclusion is, then it will
be accessible.

10:36.803 --> 10:40.840 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In terms of what extent, again,
there are
some legal procedures to go
through.

10:40.874 --> 10:46.446 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But my goal is to make it as
clear as possible
as soon as possible.

10:46.479 --> 10:52.218 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Do you have any
more information,
Mayor Roberts, about who the
victim was?

10:52.252 --> 10:56.155 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We know that the woman who said
she was his
daughter said that he had a
disability.

10:56.189 --> 10:57.991 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Do we know any more about that?

10:58.024 --> 11:03.663 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: I have not
been able to
confirm any more information
about the victim.

11:03.696 --> 11:09.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I know that there are many folks
in the community
who are stepping up, our faith
leaders, our

11:09.536 --> 11:14.941 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
community leaders, who are
calling for peace,
who are calling for patience.

11:14.974 --> 11:20.380 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Absolutely want people to
express their views,
express their frustration,
perhaps, with the

11:20.413 --> 11:22.415 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
slowness of information coming
out.

11:22.448 --> 11:26.853 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we are calling for peace and
hoping that
people will wait until it all
becomes clear

11:26.886 --> 11:28.721 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and we can get that information
out.

11:28.755 --> 11:32.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We reported just
a few moments
ago that there appeared to be
demonstrations

11:32.559 --> 11:36.362 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
forming this afternoon in
Charlotte.

11:36.396 --> 11:38.631 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What is the state of what's
going on in the
community right now?

11:38.665 --> 11:41.568 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: We have had
some gatherings.

11:41.601 --> 11:45.939 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We had a small gathering of
people in our
uptown area of people very
peacefully, very

11:45.972 --> 11:50.343 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
quietly holding up signs, Black
Lives Matter.

11:50.376 --> 11:55.982 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have a gathering of the faith
community
and some faith leaders who are
gathering in

11:56.015 --> 11:59.085 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a park who have made it very
clear this is
peaceful.

11:59.118 --> 12:06.859 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They want to express their
concern with a
story that, again, has played
out all around

12:06.893 --> 12:08.761 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the country.

12:08.795 --> 12:15.468 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And folks are very skeptical, to
be honest,
of some of the investigations
that have happened.

12:15.501 --> 12:17.737 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But we want people to express
that frustration.

12:17.770 --> 12:19.606 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We want to work with our
community.

12:19.639 --> 12:24.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have a long tradition of our
faith leaders,
of our business and community
leaders coming

12:24.143 --> 12:26.579 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
together to work through these
things.

12:26.613 --> 12:28.414 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And we have had numerous
dialogues.

12:28.448 --> 12:34.120 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have a community relations
committee that
the city has that has a process
where we can

12:34.153 --> 12:35.855 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
have these constructive
dialogues.

12:35.888 --> 12:40.093 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And finally, just
quickly,
we understand President Obama
telephoned you

12:40.126 --> 12:41.094 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
today.

12:41.127 --> 12:42.095 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Is that right?

12:42.128 --> 12:43.096 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What did he say?

12:43.129 --> 12:44.998 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: Absolutely.

12:45.031 --> 12:50.136 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I have spoken to President
Obama, and he certainly
offered any help the federal
government could

12:50.169 --> 12:52.005 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
provide.

12:52.038 --> 12:55.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There are folks in the Justice
Department,
others who have worked with
community policing

12:55.908 --> 12:59.712 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
strategies who know how to work
with communities.

12:59.746 --> 13:02.482 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I was grateful for the call.

13:02.515 --> 13:09.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Clearly, this is something our
country is
facing, and we absolutely do
need to know

13:09.756 --> 13:12.125 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
that there are racial
disparities still in
our country.

13:12.158 --> 13:17.063 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it is in our best interests
and in our
community's best interest to
work together,

13:17.096 --> 13:23.269 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to continue to be a country that
is more equal
and where everyone is treated
with dignity

13:23.302 --> 13:24.270 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and respect.

13:24.303 --> 13:26.039 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we pledge to do that here in
Charlotte.

13:26.072 --> 13:29.275 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Mayor Jennifer
Roberts, the
mayor of the city of Charlotte,
thank you

13:29.308 --> 13:30.276 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
very much.

13:30.309 --> 13:35.715 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JENNIFER ROBERTS: Thanks for
having me.

13:35.748 --> 13:48.261 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Issues of race and
justice were
also the candidates' focus on
the campaign

13:48.294 --> 13:49.562 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
trail today.

13:49.595 --> 13:50.863 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
John Yang reports.

13:50.897 --> 13:54.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And a warning: It includes
language that may
be offensive.

13:54.200 --> 14:01.340 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Donald Trump, the
self-proclaimed
law and order candidate, raised
questions

14:01.374 --> 14:06.012 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
today about the actions of a
white police
officer whose shooting of an
unarmed black

14:06.045 --> 14:10.616 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
man last week is being
investigated by the
Justice Department.

14:10.650 --> 14:15.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate:
I watched the shooting, in
particular, in

14:15.154 --> 14:21.561 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
