that.

14:43.082 --> 14:48.087 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Trump was speaking
during a conference
of pastors at a black church in
a Cleveland

14:48.121 --> 14:51.958 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
suburb.

14:51.991 --> 14:55.495 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
