promoter Don King.

14:55.528 --> 15:00.666 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
King recalled counseling Michael
Jackson about
the realities of how blacks are
viewed in

15:00.700 --> 15:04.103 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
