accidentally use
the N-word.

15:04.137 --> 15:09.108 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DON KING, Founder, Don King
Productions: if
you are rich, you are a rich
Negro.

15:09.142 --> 15:10.510 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
If you are intelligent,
intellectual, you're
an intellectual Negro.

15:10.543 --> 15:12.912 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you are a dancing and sliding
and gliding
nigger -- I mean Negro.

15:12.945 --> 15:14.180 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
