by more than

16:33.726 --> 16:35.494 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
2-1.

16:35.528 --> 16:37.864 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm John
