17:03.589 --> 17:04.557 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The rules were
different.

17:04.590 --> 17:06.392 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GARY JOHNSON: The rules were
different.

17:06.425 --> 17:09.495 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, of course, the rules were
really adopted
to make sure that a third party
would never

17:09.528 --> 17:10.963 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
