classic.

17:45.398 --> 17:48.367 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you don't get known, you
can't get on the
debate stage.

17:48.401 --> 17:49.368 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

17:49.402 --> 17:50.369 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GARY JOHNSON: It's a catch-22,
