17:52.138 --> 17:55.741 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: So, there is, as we
have seen
in lots of polls, evidence that
there are

17:55.775 --> 18:00.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
