Clearly, what we're doing is
working up to
a certain point, but, clearly,
right now,

20:00.032 --> 20:01.867 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
there's a breakdown.

20:01.901 --> 20:05.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I'm talking about the
